        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-28T21:33:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If using const dyld_all_image_infos* as recommended, this parameter should be size_t* instead of vm_size_t* or mach_vm_size_t*.\n\n(The size type should match the pointer or address type.)",
      "revId": "fbc3fd552020e02915cb8485c64d3ebe42bb2bd3",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
